Joshua trees



We decided to leave camp early, so we could see the Living Desert Museum. Never having been that way before, we took a detour through the park... Soon after here, the road descended out of the Joshua trees to the low desert.
Taken Sunday, March 16, 2003, 11:44:05am.  Original image size: 3072x1728, 7.1Mb
